{"tid":2258712,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"聽個最好笑既寵物名係咩?","createTime":"2020-10-26T09:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T20:01:02.000Z","uid":342282,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8928752a0d745aa177ab65857e43078fa9fa91","tid":2258712,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"以前女朋友做獸醫診所<br />\n佢話聽個隻好瘦既法鬥叫肥豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有隻黑色既貓叫黑豹全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有隻芝哇哇叫「狗」紋龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個男人全家6個人帶隻唐狗黎睇醫生，隻狗叫阿嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢真正個阿嫂每次聽到都笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個女仔養隻哥基，隻哥基叫咩事，醫生黎到，咩事宜家咩事呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好笑係有個阿叔養隻勁蠢勁on9異國短毛貓，叫老佛爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我女朋友有忍住笑咁問個名點黎<br />\n個阿叔話屋企好多貓，隻隻都蝦佢，成日俾貓fuck , 所以叫老fuck爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話聽過最長既名叫如來神掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻英短好鐘意打人塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3e586dbe22b792fc85ae00c43fca88247dde86","tid":2258712,"uid":1823,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"之前有個post叫臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9609ed11e9c7211913c10dd7642868f7ea0b7417","tid":2258712,"uid":137399,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"帶鼠去睇獸醫 有隻龜叫老解"},{"pid":"465d8368dd4b64bae6a9b0aa1fcb19c33879469c","tid":2258712,"uid":53730,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"隻兔叫狗強"},{"pid":"72e64f3619cda4602c94e619c7b9e339d35d2242","tid":2258712,"uid":52539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"巴打隻兔仔 狗強 狗勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8577f95603911dc474fe0278164979aa53528d13","tid":2258712,"uid":7493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"馬鷹狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599acda489d0a13d5bc5f7f7b685195133a3af1e","tid":2258712,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"隻狗叫牛油"},{"pid":"acf69067b692f346454c9a4b191835d475dbb7f8","tid":2258712,"uid":6599,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"隻貓叫喪彪"},{"pid":"8d661d736c610e5a3daaf56b8e722d6026070fad","tid":2258712,"uid":6599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acf69067b692f346454c9a4b191835d475dbb7f8","tid":2258712,"uid":6599,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"隻貓叫喪彪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"布偶貓"},{"pid":"b7b3725e3b4f67410083ee3ca5beb98c03424219","tid":2258712,"uid":264172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"維尼 <br />\n林奠"},{"pid":"0723b44894963452c951b064072c29a1f3e1cc36","tid":2258712,"uid":321977,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"梅艷芳從小就喜歡狗，後來一次性養了三條狗，她為這三條狗分別起了獨特的名字：Eric、倫伯、阿叻。"},{"pid":"5a6410531ea9c9ff280821652ca3ea1ce710fdae","tid":2258712,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"自撚獅"},{"pid":"b7152df436ecabc8dab0956fb7a27bacdba85f87","tid":2258712,"uid":128102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-